<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied></hi> kopparakecari parmaku vāṇṭu 6 Āva
<lb n="2" break="no"/>tu tirucceṅkoṭṭu tiruvoṇakkaṇapperumakkaḷ
<lb n="3"/>kaiyil tiṅkaḷ toṟum Oḻukkamāka Irupatu <hi rend="grantha">brā</hi>
<lb n="4" break="no"/><hi rend="grantha">hma</hi>ṇarai ca<hi rend="grantha">ntrā</hi>titta niṉṟatoṉṟāka Ūṭṭu
<lb n="5" break="no"/>vatāka Īroṭṭu ta<hi rend="grantha"><unclear>nta</unclear></hi>maṇikaṇṭi <unclear>O</unclear>ṭaiyamantā
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ḷukkāka Araṭṭa nakkar makaṉ tiruvoṇak kaṇapperumakkaḷ
<lb n="7"/>vacam vaitta poṉ Irupatiṉ kaḻañcu poṉṉu
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ṅkoṇṭu Iruvatu <hi rend="grantha">brāhma</hi>ṇarai Ippoṉṉiṉ pa
<lb n="9" break="no"/>licaikoṇṭu Ūṭṭuvatāka Eṉṟom tiruvoṇak ka
<lb n="10" break="no"/>ṇapperumakkaḷ <unclear>ḷom Itu Iṟa</unclear>kkuvāṉ <unclear>taṉṉeccama</unclear>
<lb n="11" break="no"/>ṟuvāṉ kāttāṉaṭi Eṉṟalai meliṉa <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
</p>

